    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >欲入此门者，须先弃希冀</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《天底》是一款黑暗Roguelike卡牌构筑冒险游戏，它那燃烧着地狱之火的艺术风格中包含着许多怪异惊奇的灵感，其中受但丁《神曲》的影响最为深刻。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >身为七宗罪的化身之一，你需要杀出一条通向传说中地狱之城天底的血路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1535100/extras/dbecb452f6d8c62954687fb1405afae0.poster.avif?t=1758301612\" width=600 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1535100/extras/dbecb452f6d8c62954687fb1405afae0.webm?t=1758301612\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1535100/extras/dbecb452f6d8c62954687fb1405afae0.mp4?t=1758301612\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🔥 双面卡牌</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 卡牌对战中，你的每张卡牌均可通过两种方式打出，其效果取决于卡牌颜色：蓝色或红色。平衡使用这些卡牌能够帮助你积累优势，不过要小心，你的每次动作都会引发敌人不同的反应。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1535100/extras/c67643904c27bddee6d33a5274129b12.poster.avif?t=1758301612\" width=600 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1535100/extras/c67643904c27bddee6d33a5274129b12.webm?t=1758301612\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1535100/extras/c67643904c27bddee6d33a5274129b12.mp4?t=1758301612\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🔥 卡牌构筑</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 在旅途中收集红色和蓝色能力，并将它们组合为独一无二的双面卡牌，以你的方式调整卡组以便应对连绵不绝的挑战，全力活下去。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🔥 扩张城市</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 在探索中手机资源，扩张天底城市，解锁新角色、新卡牌以及新的商人。扩张你的地下王朝，提升击败领主的可能性，解锁新的罪人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1535100/extras/52d4d80e8d531f8ca546bbb9912f7fd7.poster.avif?t=1758301612\" width=600 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1535100/extras/52d4d80e8d531f8ca546bbb9912f7fd7.webm?t=1758301612\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1535100/extras/52d4d80e8d531f8ca546bbb9912f7fd7.mp4?t=1758301612\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🔥 致命罪行</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 每位罪人都有着独有的敌人类型，他们将极大程度上改变你的游戏方式。了解敌人，形成策略，击败他们，这将是构建强力卡组并在战斗中生存的关键。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1535100/extras/3ba2b0a78b091d4c0ce6d50d8cba0e3a.poster.avif?t=1758301612\" width=600 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1535100/extras/3ba2b0a78b091d4c0ce6d50d8cba0e3a.webm?t=1758301612\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1535100/extras/3ba2b0a78b091d4c0ce6d50d8cba0e3a.mp4?t=1758301612\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🔥 与众不同的旅程</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 在前往天底的旅途中，请勿只顾匆匆向前，花点时间欣赏周围那惊怖绝伦的景色。从来自《神曲》的奇观异景，到《罪恶之城》的黑白美学，再到《地狱男爵》风格的角色设计，你可能会觉得一切似曾相识，只不过他们早已融为一体。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1535100/extras/4d58607781cb257212c08be7a2785661.poster.avif?t=1758301612\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1535100/extras/4d58607781cb257212c08be7a2785661.webm?t=1758301612\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1535100/extras/4d58607781cb257212c08be7a2785661.mp4?t=1758301612\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
